data.description: GREAT FOR TWO HOUSEHOLDS OR INVESTMENT PROPERTY! Cute, wood framed home on 1.236 acres with 3-4 bedrooms, 2 baths. Also includes a 2015 doublewide mobile home with 4-5 bedrooms, 2 baths. Mobile home was recently moved in was in the process of remodel when sellers had to move. Work is unfinished, but would not take much to finish. Property also has 2400 sq ft shop with concrete floor and electricity. Small storage shed with a dirt floor. Large, shaded yard.
